      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the S54B32 power plant, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear, high-revving power band. Mechanically, the vehicle has been fastidiously maintained with a documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the telepathic feedback this chassis is legendary for. Finished in pristine Carbon Black, this is a turn-key, investment-quality specimen for the purist.",
